Class PlaylistItemColumns

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.database.PlaylistItemColumns
  • public class PlaylistItemColumns extends java.lang.Object
    The columns available to clients for querying the playlist item cursor for a playlist. Note that none of these columns can be updated via the content provider.
